title: Nas - Illmatic 10th Anniversary Platinum Edition
description:
Illmatic is the debut album of rapper Nas, released on April 19, 1994.
In 2004 Nas released a 10th Anniversary Platinum Edition of Illmatic.
The 10th Anniversary Platinum Edition includes a second disc with six additional tracks. (four of them are remixes). 

All files have been scanned with Avira.
No viruses, trojans, malware, or spyware.
The files are in .mp3 format.
Included is the cover of the album in .jpg format.

This is a great album. 

Enjoy.
